title: Dennis Lyxen from INVSN/AC4/Refused
itunes:title: Dennis Lyxen from INVSN/AC4/Refused
description:
I couldn't wait to bring you guys this great conversation I had with Dennis Lyxen, the vocalist for bandsINVSN/AC4/Refused & International Noise Conspiracy. It was a very enlightening chat about his surreal moments with Refused's reunion tour, credibility and never asking for permission to do anything.
